11-11-11 is a 2011 supernatural horror film written and directed by darren lynn bousman . the film is set on 11:11 on the 11th day of the 11th month and concerning an entity from another world that enters the earthly realm through heaven 's 11th gate . the film was released on november 11 , 2011 in 17 theaters domestically . it was distributed by columbia pictures in north america , though most of its revenues were generated from foreign showings .